      "rationale": "Three QoIs (construct stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm displacement) were compared using both mean percentage difference and the E/uval metric per ASME V&V 40 Section 9. All E/uval values (1.31, 1.62, 1.44) are below the 1.96 threshold. Percentage differences (4.2%, 6.8%, 5.5%) are below the 10% bound. Quantitative output comparison is comprehensive. Achieved level meets required level."
