      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in the FDA guidance for ASTM F1717 pedicle screw testing and directly address the clinical performance question of structural adequacy under physiological loading. QoIs are well-established in the regulatory context. Achieved level meets required level."
